The REDUCE HTN: REINFORCE study is being conducted to determine whether the Vessix Reduce cent Catheter and Vessix cent Generator for the treatment of uncontrolled hypertension (off-treatment office systolic blood pressure 150 mmHg and 180 mmHg) shows acceptable performance at 8 weeks when compared to a masked procedure (renal angiogram).

